
Masquerain	 A bug type Pokémon

MASQUERAIN intimidates enemies with 
the eyelike patterns on its antennas. 
 This POKéMON flaps its four wings to 
freely fly in any direction - even sideways 
and backwards - as if it were a helicopter. 

